Package org.odpi.openmetadata.conformance.beans

Class OpenMetadataConformanceProfileSummary

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.conformance.beans.OpenMetadataConformanceProfileSummary
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class OpenMetadataConformanceProfileSummary extends Object implements Serializable
OpenMetadataConformanceProfileSummary provides a summary of the assessment of a technology's conformance to an open metadata conformance profile.
